%section#commons
	%article
		%h5 Welcome, UX collective
		%section
			%p 
				Hi, UX2.0 is a project funded by 
				%a{:href=>"http://www.jisc.ac.uk/whatwedo/programmes/inf11.aspx"} JISC
				(Information Environment Programme 2009-11) 
				to undertake research and development to enhance user experience of 
				digital libraries, through technological developments that are centered on 
				usability inspection and evaluation.
	%article
		%h5 Usability Inspection of Digital Libraries
		%section
			%p 
				The project has conducted a heuristics evaluation on a selection of digital libraries. 
				The study not only informs the subsequent evaluation work of UX2.0, it is generally useful for 
				the JISC Community and includes a survey of emerging interaction design patterns in digital libraries.
			%p
				:markdown
					More from the [full report](http://bit.ly/ux2inspectionreport) and 
					a [recent publication](http://www.ariadne.ac.uk/issue63/paterson-low/).
